requestBody.description:
Search and return the list of users using a special filter. 
           Example, if you want return all users and admins {"search": "","status": 0,"role": ["admin","user"]} 
           Example if you want return all admins{'search': '','status': 0,'role': ['admin']}
           Status has 4 positions: 0 - All positions, 1 - Active users, 2 - Requested users, 3 - Locked users.
           An instance of the interface representing the users with specified filter property
